structure.unit: A AUTOMATED MOTOR VEHICLE REGISTRATION SYSTEM

law.catch_line: Definitions to be consistent with KRS 186.010.
law.text: Unless the context requires otherwise, terms used in this chapter shall be defined, where applicable, as provided by KRS 186.010.
